data.description: Welcome Home!  Come Enjoy waterfront  access to the Clinch River right from  your own back yard!  Rarely do you find 1.44 acres of LEVEL  land  with a brick /Vinyl basement ranch home in the South Clinton area ''PLUS'' a bonus of - 3 extra outbuildings - 26x40 Detached Garage/Workshop, 22x24 Red Pole Barn w/ Stalls, 28x26 Detached Garage Workshop. This estate has been very well maintained and first time offered,  located minutes from Historic downtown Clinton and Melton Hill Lake
